event.title: Monthly Fellowship Meeting in Linz, Austria
event.body: The FSFE Fellowship Group Linz meets in the Hackspace DevLoL, Hofgasse 19, 4020 Linz. Our meetings start at 18:30 (CET) and the Agenda will start at 19:00 (MEZ). Everyone, who is interessted in the FSFE or free Software in general is invited to come to our meeting. We are pleased to meet you there.
